Step 2— Create new elastic search indices
We will be creating two indices called autocomplete and hacker. hacker
index will be using a template called search_engine_template.

Index templates allow you to define templates that will automatically be applied when new indices are created.
The templates include both settings and mappings and a simple pattern template that controls
whether the template should be applied to the new index.

run create_new_index.py

